Method Name: Substructure matches from experimental data (pKa Prospector to perform a substructure search on each molecule, an estimate for the macro pKa based on matching the ionizable groups identified by pKa prospector. I basically just did a pKa prospector search with a little bit of discretion on which match to use and made up an ÒSEMÓ based on how similar the molecule in the database was.)
Gaussian and separate fitting for neutral to negative and for positive to neutral transformations
